      <title>特朗普SPAC投资者在内幕交易案中认罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-spac-investor-pleads-guilty-to-insider-trading</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两名被控在空白支票公司进行内幕交易的投资者承认了一项证券欺诈罪，该公司将唐纳德·特朗普的社交媒体初创公司公开化，距离审判不到一个月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/trump-spac-investor-pleads-guilty-to-insider-trading</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:51:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
